English: I see that at last there is a real knight among all of you.
Spanish: Veo que por fin hay un verdadero caballero entre todos vosotros.

English: Now hand me the spears, future servant of the greatest JumpBorn.
Spanish: Ahora dame las lanzas, futuro sirviente del JumpBorn mas grande.

English: You have no idea what I went through to get them, right?
Spanish: No tienes idea de lo que he pasado para conseguirlas, verdad?

English: Now I'm going to show you the power of the spears of the legendary JUMPBORNS!
Spanish: !Ahora te mostrare el poder de las lanzas de los legendarios JUMPBORNS!
